Jivelite applet to control ALSA sound devices (analogous to alsamixer)

Install: Add the repository URL 

http://ralph_irving.users.sourceforge.net/repo.xml

to the Settings->Plugin->Additional Repositories at the bottom.

On the jive device to go Settings->Advanced->Applet Installer and install ALSA Mixer.

Restart jivelite.

Alsa Mixer can then be found in Settings->Audio Settings.
